/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "SYS_Func" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "SYS_Func"
(
"FuncID" NUMBER(10) not null,
"MenuID" NUMBER(10) not null,
"FuncCode" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"FuncName" INTEGER not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP default SYSDATE not null,
constraint PK_SYS_FUNC primary key ("FuncID")
);

comment on table "SYS_Func" is
'控制页面上功能（按钮或展现区域）';

comment on column "SYS_Func"."FuncName" is
'0，1，2共3级';

comment on column "SYS_Func"."Enable" is
'1: 启用
0: 停用';

alter table "SYS_Func"
add constraint FK_SYS_FUNC_2_SYS_MENU_PK foreign key ("MenuID")
references "SYS_Menu" ("MenuID");
